MS.S: *PassPushPosh* is a PowerShell Module for interfacing with the Password Pusher secure password / string sharing application, primarily through pwpush.com. It supports creating, retrieving, and deleting anonymous and authenticated pushes, links in any supported language, and getting Push and Dashboard data for authenticated users._x000D__x000A__x000D__x000A_Cmdlets provide clear responses to errors, support additional messaging via -Debug and -Verbose, transaction testing via -Whatif and -Confirm, and in general try to be as "Powershell-y" as possible.
